Какие из WSGI приложений корректны ?

A)

def app(env, start_response):
    start_response('200 OK', [('Content-Type', 'text/plain')])
    return  ['Hello, world!']

B)

def application(env, start_response):
    start_response('200 OK')
    return  ['Hello, world!']

C)

def application(env, start_response):
    start_response('200 OK', [('Content-Type', 'text/plain')])
    return  'Hello, world!'

D)

def application(env):
    return  ['Hello, world!']

A
C